    "Html": "<p>Hi Waleed,</p>\r\n<p>Based on my understanding of your scenario, you need to call the <strong>ModuleManager&rsquo;s</strong> <strong>LoadModule</strong> method in order your <em>AVTModule</em> gets loaded.</p>\r\n<p>You can read more about how to load modules on demand <a href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ff921068(PandP.40).aspx#sec8\">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p>I hope you find this information useful.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks,</p>\r\n<p>Miguel Bronzovic<br /><a href=\"http://blogs.southworks.net/mbronzovic\">http://blogs.southworks.net/mbronzovic</a></p>",
